INFO: ['Dear students,\xa0', 'The inconsistency comes from the spec of a Broadcast call vs a Broadcast implementation. If a client/node calls Broadcast, the *Broadcast call* does not have a destination, because it implicitly means "send to all". But, the *Broadcast implementation* consists of sending Rumor messages to some chosen destinations.\xa0', 'We hope this clarifies the issue, otherwise please write back.', 'Best regards,', 'Cristina']
